Store %post scripts
-------------------

Can we get the %post scripts and store them in a directory in the
appliance?


Some features of supermin 4 which were cut in supermin 5
--------------------------------------------------------

 - Frugalware / pacman-g2: requires 'pactree' tool to be packaged

 - write an initrd file (ie. '-f cpio')

 - --user/--group options
